Summer Michelle Hansen, 32, of California was sentenced in court on Friday; she was a teacher at Centennial High School . 
 She entered a guilty plea in February to 16 felony counts including seven counts of oral copulation of a minor and six counts of statutory rape . 
 If she had been convicted at trial, she could have faced 13 years in prison . 
 Hansen was arrested in June 2013 after a student came forward and said he had sex with her . 
 Prosecutors said the sex acts occurred between May 2012 and 2013 . 
 